<h1 class="mt-3 mb-2">GopherExchange Privacy Policy</h1>

<div class="container">
    <p>GopherExchange takes the privacy of its users seriously. The details below outline what we collect, how it is
        used
        and
        how you can opt out.</p>

    <h2>What is collected</h2>
    <p>To make GopherExchange function for everybody this is what we collect:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Your Goucher College email address.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Why we collect that</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>This service is only authorized to the members of the Goucher College community. For
            transparency and
            security
            your Goucher email verifies your identity. Furthermore, your email address is used so that other community
            members
            are
            able to contact you about your listing.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>How to opt out</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>For any time and for any reason, you are freely able to delete your account by going
            into your Account page
            and
            clicking Delete Account.</li>
    </ul>
</div>
