    <ul>
        <li><strong>You</strong>: refers to you, the end user using the service.</li>
        <li><strong>Administrator Team</strong>: refers to administrator team responsible for enforcing Terms of Service
            and curating the instance of GopherExchange.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Terms of Service</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Obey all Goucher College policies</strong>: As this is a service meant for the Goucher community,
            all
            Goucher College policies, including, but not limited to, Student Code of Conduct, are still in effect.</li>
